        <lg type="stanza" n="6">
          <l n="1">Salutation with thanksgiving to your hands and to your elbows,</l>
          <l n="2">To your arms and to your forearms, the seat of greatness.</l>
          <l n="3">Covenant of Mercy, Mary, as you saved</l>
          <l n="4">The sinful eater of men through a measure of cool water,</l>
          <l n="5">Let your covenant save me, a sick man.</l>
